    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#quttypes">负担[fùdān]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#ezjqbqsy">负担[fùdān]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="#quttypes">负担[fùdān]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p> [charge]∶费用,开支</p></li><li><p> [burden;encumbrance]∶承受的责任</p><p>家庭负担</p><p>精神负担</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="#ezjqbqsy">负担[fùdān]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[bear;shoulder] 承当 [责任、工作、费用等]</p><p>全家开支由他一人负担</p><p>她在公司里负担全部抄写工作</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
